Load college basketball games for a given season

load_games.Rd

Pull in all college basketball games tracked by collegebasketballdata.com for a given season

Usage

load_games(seasons = most_recent_season())

Arguments

seasons

an integer of seasons to fetch data for. Defaults to the most recent season. Pass in TRUE to fetch all seasons.

Value

a dataframe of all games in the specified season(s).

Examples
